# kcan-synthetic.crtd — synthetic KCAN fixture for the decode pipeline replay test.
#
# Fictional VW e-Golf, parked in Berlin (Brandenburg Gate area).
# No real vehicle data — safe for public repositories.
#
# Scenario : ignition on, parked, unlocked, no charger connected.
# Location : 52.5163 N  13.3777 E  (fictional)
